  "article_text": "Welcome to the Star Atlas weekly recap from the Intergalactic Herald. Below is what happened with Star Atlas this past week.\nWe are looking for guests to be on our podcast. The podcast is a discussion of the past week’s news about Star Atlas. If you are interested in being on the podcast, please contact us.\nWe are launching a Star Atlas merch store. Please check it out at Intergalactic Gear.\nWe are creating a “non-guild” guild. If you are interested in learning more, please go to Intergalactic Coalition.\nIf you would like to support our efforts, donations can be sent to intergalacticherald.sol\nStar Atlas Starbased: The New Atlas Prime Features\nBeyond the Horizon posted a video about the new Altas Prime feature in SAGE Starbased.\nSTAR ATLAS #232 AUTOMATED CRAFTING IS HERE!\nMetaVerse Explorer posted a video of Star Atlas updates.\nStar Atlas: Buying REAL-LIFE Food with $ I Made In-Game\nBeyond the Horizon posted a video of buying coffee with ATLAS.\nMetaverse Nomads #145 – Bodhi [TREE] Interview – Star Atlas\nMetaverse Nomads posted their weekly Star Atlas livestream.\nWEEKLY STAR ATLAS NEWSLETTER #128\nAephia published their weekly Star Atlas newsletter.\nLore Keepers #2\nStar Atlas TV posted a replay of the latest Lore Keepers event.\nThe Atlas Brew #110\nStar Atlas TV posted a replay of the latest Atlas Brew event.\nSuperPhoenix DAO WhitePaper – TLDR\nBeth posted a video recap of the SuperPhoenix DAO whitepaper.\nSTAR ATLAS #233 Upcoming Changes YOU NEED TO KNOW!\nMetaVerse Explorer posted a video about the upcoming changes to SAGE Starbased.",
